title: S2 Ep10: Food or food stamps?
itunes:title: Food or food stamps?
description: Indonesia recently started providing vouchers instead of rice to millions of households. Elan Satriawan of National Team for Acceleration of Poverty Reduction tells Tim Phillips that this has made it possible to target aid better and is cheaper to administer too.
